DATA ATTRIBUTION

Restaurant data contained in this repository is derived from the French
Wikipedia article "Cauchemar en cuisine (France)"
(https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cauchemar_en_cuisine_(France)) and is provided
under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 license
(https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/). The names "Cauchemar en
cuisine", "M6", "Studio 89 Productions", and "Philippe Etchebest" are
referenced for descriptive purposes only; all trademarks and related rights
belong to their respective owners. This atlas is an independent, non-official,
documentary project with no commercial affiliation.

